cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB 

The paper deals with the retrieval and analysis of text data from the World Wide Web, which is a common topic in Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of topic signatures and hierarchical clustering also involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses the limitations of existing ontologies, which is a topic in both machine learning and database systems (cs.LG and cs.DB).
